s-widget-api-consent-settings-313x281.jpg 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings.jpg 1476w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></p>\n<p id=\"caption-attachment-295602\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Google Maps Widget API Consent Settings</p>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/google-maps-widget/#heading-global-settings\">Google Maps Widget Consent Prompt Documentation</a></p>\n<h3>Enhanced by SiteOrigin Premium</h3>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/?featured_addon=plugin/map-styles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SiteOrigin Premium Map Styles</a> addon provides three additional settings:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Consent prompt text color.</li>\n<li>Consent prompt text background color.</li>\n<li>Consent prompt background image.</li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_295599\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-295599\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-699x584.jpg\" alt=\"oogle Maps API Consent Settings\" width=\"699\" height=\"584\" class=\"size-large wp-image-295599\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-699x584.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-300x251.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-768x642.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-1050x877.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-313x262.jpg 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings.jpg 1448w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></p>\n<p id=\"caption-attachment-295599\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Consent Prompt Design Settings</p